<section id="fs-id1171360403956" class="critical-thinking">
<title>Gagnrýnin hugsun</title>
<exercise id="fs-id1171360161140">
<problem id="fs-id1171359070868">
<para id="fs-id1171360231286">Berðu saman hegðun veiru utan frumu og innan hennar.</para>
